'''Yulu''' is an ethnic group in [[Central African Republic]], 
[[Democratic Republic of the Congo]], [[Sudan]] and [[South Sudan]]. They speak [[Yulu language|Yulu]], a Nilo-Saharan language. The population of this group is at several thousand.

